        "accordion_XxNWpm": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "name": "t:names.accordion",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "caret",
            "dividers": true,
            "type_preset": "h5",
            "inherit_color_scheme": true,
            "color_scheme": "",
            "border": "none",
            "border_width": 1,
            "border_opacity": 100,
            "border_radius": 0,
            "padding-block-start": 0,
            "padding-block-end": 0,
            "padding-inline-start": 0,
            "padding-inline-end": 0
          },
          "blocks": {
            "accordion_row_nkHNrP": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How does the at-home saliva test work?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_7dezVj": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Simply collect your saliva samples at home using the tubes provided in your kit, fill out the symptom assessment, and mail everything back with the prepaid return label. Your samples are analyzed by a certified lab.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "paragraph",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_7dezVj"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_e7DhwY": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "How long does it take to get my results?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_PxVxF8": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Most results are ready within 10–12 business days after the lab receives your sample</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_PxVxF8"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_7RW6TH": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What hormones does the test measure?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_R3cyeb": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>The test measures estradiol, progesterone, testosterone, and your estrogen-to-progesterone ratio. It also includes a comprehensive symptom analysis covering thyroid, adrenal, metabolic, and sex hormone health.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_R3cyeb"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_QpjRGH": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Is the consultation really included?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_eA7nxK": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes! Every test kit includes an essential complimentary consultation with a Hormone Expert who will review your results, explain what they mean, and help determine if a personalized BHRT plan is right for you.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_eA7nxK"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_iWfA6H": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Who is this test for?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_mq9fFM": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>This test is ideal for women over 35 who are experiencing symptoms of perimenopause or menopause — such as fatigue, brain fog, weight gain, sleep issues, low libido, or mood changes — and want real answers about what’s going on with their hormones.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
                    "background": false,
                    "background_color": "#00000026",
                    "corner_radius": 0,
                    "padding-block-start": 0,
                    "padding-block-end": 0,
                    "padding-inline-start": 0,
                    "padding-inline-end": 0
                  },
                  "blocks": {}
                }
              },
              "block_order": [
                "text_mq9fFM"
              ]
            },
            "accordion_row_TH3HdB": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "What happens after my consultation?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "none",
                "width": 20
              },
              "blocks": {
                "text_DLVafP": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>After reviewing your results together, your Hormone Expert will help you understand your options, including whether bioidentical hormone replacement therapy (BHRT) could be beneficial for you. You’ll leave with a clear plan to start feeling like yourself again.</p>",
                    "width": "100%",
                    "max_width": "none",
                    "alignment": "left",
                    "type_preset": "rte",
                    "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
                    "font_size": "1rem",
                    "line_height": "normal",
                    "letter_spacing": "normal",
                    "case": "none",
                    "wrap": "pretty",
                    "color": "var(--color-foreground)",
